OL,6,FOnly half of fathers avail of
OL,7,Fpaternity leave and a quarter of men
OL,8,Ftake parent's leave compared with two-
OL,9,Fthirds of mothers, research has
OL,10,Frevealed.
OL,12,FThe report from the Irish Human Rights
OL,13,Fand Equality Commission (IHREC) and
OL,14,Fthe Economic and Social Research
OL,15,FInstitute (ESRI) found that while the
OL,16,Frecent introduction of paternity leave
OL,17,Fand parent's leave in Ireland has been
OL,18,Fpositive, the take-up rates of the
OL,19,Fbenefits remain low.
