OL,6,FThe report also calls for structural
OL,7,Finequality between women and men to be
OL,8,Faddressed, saying that Ireland must
OL,9,Ffind a new relationship between paid
OL,10,Femployment, care work and gender roles.
OL,12,FThe report, entitled Child Related
OL,13,FLeave: Usage and Implications for
OL,14,FGender Equality, examines the usage of
OL,15,Fchild-related leave benefits in
OL,16,FIreland and their implications for
OL,17,Fgender equality in the workplace.
