OL,6,FTake-up was also higher for those
OL,7,Fworking in larger companies where a
OL,8,Freplacement might be more readily
OL,9,Favailable.
OL,11,FThe report also explores societal
OL,12,Fnorms and workplace attitudes towards
OL,13,Fchild-related leave.
OL,15,FA survey experiment found high levels
OL,16,Fof support for ensuring that fathers
OL,17,Fhave 100% of their earnings covered
OL,18,Fwhile on leave and for ring-fencing
OL,19,Fpart of child-related leave for
OL,20,Ffathers only.
