OL,6,FThe report suggests ways to improve
OL,7,Fthe take-up of child-related leave
OL,8,Fbenefits and promote gender equality.
OL,10,FThe report found that relying on
OL,11,Femployers to top up parents' incomes
OL,12,Fresults in a large variation in how
OL,13,Fmuch of pre-birth earnings are covered
OL,14,Fduring leave as top-ups vary
OL,15,Fsignificantly across different
OL,16,Femployers.
OL,18,FIt also said that promoting awareness
OL,19,Fof leave entitlements among parents,
OL,20,Fparticularly fathers, would increase
OL,21,Ftake-up rates.
